Following text  will be in xymonmon developer FAQ in the future.

How do I help improving the xymonmon books ?

1. Get a developer account from xymonmon project admin(Henrik Stoner) to have svn write access.
2. check out xymonmon source.
   2.1 books source in in xymonmon branches.
   svn co https://xymonmon.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/xymon hobbitmon 
3. using xymonmon-rtfm as an example
   3.1 "cd xymonmon/branches/tjyang/src/books/xymon-rtfm/en"
   3.2 edit the tex file that has an typo of "Hobbitmon" as "Hobbit" 
       Ex: perl -pi -e 's!Hobbit!Hobbitmon!' about.tex 
   3.3 make

[tjyang@ibm en]$ make
mkdir -p pdf/
TEXINPUTS=./: pdflatex -interaction batchmode -output-directory pdf/ -jobname xymon-RTFM 00book.tex || (rm -f pdf/hobbit-RTFM.pdf; exit 1)
