   3.4  the new version of xymon-RTFM.pdf got generated.

[tjyang@ibm en]$ ls -l pdf/*.pdf
-rw-rw-r-- 1 tjyang tjyang 9244471 2008-08-11 10:06 pdf/xymon-RTFM.pdf
