[tjyang@ibm en]$ 

  3.6  commit the change. you can see the changes got uploaded to SVN server on sourceforge.net.
  
[tjyang@ibm en]$ svn commit -m "correct type of Hobbitmon from Hobbit"
Sending        en/about.tex
Sending        en/pdf/xymon-RTFM.pdf
